<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>I Told You So - hannesnagel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div id="site-nav"></div>

    <main class="page">
        <section class="hero">
            <p class="sub-header">iOS App</p>
            <h1>I Told You So</h1>
            <p class="lead">Capture predictions, friendly bets, and bold claims before everyone changes their story. Settle the outcome later and keep the receipt.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a class="nav-link" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6763559466">App Store</a>
                <a class="nav-link" href="/i-told-you-so/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Support</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="work">
            <div class="section-head">
                <p class="sub-header">What it does</p>
                <h2>Receipts for the moments people forget.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="cards">
                <article class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Record it fast</h3>
                        <p>Write down who said what, what they predicted, and what is at stake.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Settle it later</h3>
                        <p>Come back when reality catches up and mark who was right.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Share the receipt</h3>
                        <p>Create a clean proof card for the group chat.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="footer-cta">
            <h2>Questions or support?</h2>
            <div class="links">
                <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
                <a href="/i-told-you-so/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/components.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
